@5200 = ~Eh? What’s this? Hah! I’ve heard tell o’ such a trinket before. Looks like it fits that old elven buckler, the Leafrunner. A fine piece, that. Hand me both bits, and I’ll see it made whole again — strong as ever. Won’t come cheap, mind ye: 7500 gold. But you’ll be gettin’ a right sturdy toy for yer coin!~
